      <title>Conda 指定安装目录｜完全修改huggingface/torch等框架的.cache目录</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/2024/12/conda-%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9huggingface/torch%E7%AD%89%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E7%9A%84.cache%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95/</link>
